data.description: REDUCED PRICE!!! This open and spacious floorplan offers a large open living, kitchen, and dining area with a fireplace, 4 bedrooms, 3 FULL baths. The Kitchen features a large flat island, granite counters, electric appliances to include double ovens, microwave, dishwasher and cooktop. From linen to walk in closets, lots of storage. Bedroom 2 has a mother-in-law/guest room plan with its own private shower. The master suite includes a jetted tub, double walk in shower, large vanity with dual sinks and an oversized walk in master closet. This plan is completed on the outside with a covered back patio great for entertaining lots of storage space and a 3 car garage!
